Output demo/demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 950
Set Height 550
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Type "# 1. Run the readiness gate"
Enter
Sleep 800ms

Type "./demo/demo-replay.sh"
Enter
Sleep 18s

Type "# Exit code 0 = safe to route traffic"
Enter
Sleep 2s
